Create a hierarchy of classes for storing information about human resources of a
company.
Create a 3-level hierarchy composed of at least 20 different employees of all the kinds
(i.e. trainees, workers and managers).

Please deliver the following functionality:
1. Preparing payroll for all the employees;
2. Searching for the highest salary.
3. Searching for employees subordinates of the given manager;
4. Searching for employees who earn more than 1000 PLN.

Create a simple interface for workers and managers.